Caroline Loeb https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caroline_Loeb 0 Caroline Loeb (born 5 October 1955 in Neuilly-sur-Seine) is a French actress, radio host, singer, and director. She is particularly known for her 1980s hit C'est la ouate. Caroline_Loeb ( born_5_October_1955 in Neuilly-sur-Seine ) is a_French_actress , radio_host , singer , and director .
